posting_body: ['Beds: 2!!!Bath: 1!!', 'Available Date: 08/07/2022!', 'Pet: ok Pets!', 'Newly remodeled luxury apartment two bedrooms shower and bath marble floors marble countertops cherry wood floors quiet neighborhood one exit away from cape cod plenty of parking 650 a month includes water.', 'Minutes to downtown, 95, and located in a cute suburban neighborhood.', 'There are trails nearby, and the home is right next to the cape cod park.', 'Rent is $690.00/month, and tenants are responsible for all utilities, plus snow removal and lawn care.no security deposit.', 'A/C, Heat, hot water, and electricity are included in this studio, kitchen with lots of cabinet space, bath with shower and 1 car parking available for 9/1.', 'This apartment is located on Long Island walk to restaurants and shopping and a quick commute to Rt 95 and 99.']
